org.icij.datashare.imageio.jpx

Class JPXImageReaderSpi

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.imageio.spi.IIOServiceProvider
      • javax.imageio.spi.ImageReaderWriterSpi
        • javax.imageio.spi.ImageReaderSpi
          • org.icij.datashare.imageio.jpx.JPXImageReaderSpi
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RegisterableService

    public class JPXImageReaderSpi
extends ImageReaderSpi
    This class shims support for JPX format images until a fix for jai-imageio-jpeg2000 issue #8 is released. It does this by wrapping the J2KImageReaderSpi provided by that package.
